14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 2 O.S. 2021, Section 5-4.2, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 5-4.2. As used in the Homemade Food Freedom Act:
17 1. "Home food establishment" shall mean a business on the
18 premises of a residence in which homemade food products are created
19 for sale or resale if the business has gross annual sales of
20 prepared food of less than Seventy-five Thousand Dollars
21 ($75,000.00) Three Hundred Thousand Dollars ($300,000.00). Gross
22 annual sales includes all sales of prepared food produced by the
23 business at any location;
